data: It was three o’clock, but the luncheon the Kinneys were giving at the Country Club had survived the passing of less leisurely patrons and now dominated the house.
Nicholson, Meredith, 1866-1947; Taffs, C. H. (Charles H.), 1876-1964 [Illustrator]
